## 1. The Three Pillars

A world-class PWA must be **Reliable**, **Fast**, and **Engaging**:

| Pillar | What It Means | Key Technologies |
|:---|:---|:---|
| **Reliable** | Loads instantly even on flaky networks; works offline | Service Worker, Cache API, IndexedDB |
| **Fast** | Responds to interactions in < 100ms; renders in < 2.5s | Code splitting, lazy loading, AVIF/WebP images |
| **Engaging** | Feels like a native app; re-engages users | Web Push API, `display: standalone`, smooth animations |

